item.title: Ice Hockey gear up for Varsity
item.author: Steven J Basher,
item.description: Tonight, the Imperial Devils Ice Hockey team take on the UCL Yetis in the 3rd annual “London Ice Varsity”. The Devils will be eager to retain their unbeaten record, having triumphed two years in a row so far. Facing off at 20:00 at Streatham Ice Arena, one of London’s great sporting rivalries will …
